Our client is a Financial Institution, they are currently seeking for an Assistant Manager (Operations)  to join their team.


Responsibilities


To perform loan origination, eligibility assessment, documentation, administration and customer service duties;
To monitor the performance of the appointed servicers and agents;
To prepare management statistics and reports;
To identify rooms and propose recommendation for process re-engineering and risk control;
To provide support for ad-hoc tasks and projects

Responsibilities:


Degree holder in Finance, Business Administration or equivalent;
A minimum of 5 years’ solid experience in mortgage loans operations;
Highly responsible, attentive to details with high degree of accuracy and with strong analytical skills;
A good team player with positive thinking, self motivated, proactive working attitude, eager to learn and to take up new responsibilities;
Good command of spoken English and Chinese, proficiency in Putonghua will be an asset; and
Strong PC skills in MS Excel and MS Access.
*Candidate(s) with less experience will be considered as Senior Associate / Associate.
Interested candidates, please send your resume (MS Word document) including employment history, present and expected salary to us.


For more jobs, please visit our website: www.delken.com.hk. 

