Responsibilities:

Responsible for the overall daily operation;
Preparation of Credit Reports/Credit Recommendations/Credit Documentation;
Maintain good relationship with customers, vendors and business partners;
Handle emails, live chats, inbound and outbound calls of customers and vendors enquiries in a proactive and positive manner;
Evaluate problems / issues raised by customers or vendors and provide solution effectively to build customer loyalty;
Handle enquiries / complaints of customers;
Participate in projects on new process/service development, automation of new process and system enhancement / UAT to improve operational efficiency.

