Diploma/ Associate degree holder or above;
Minimum 1 year of retail banking / phone banking / financial industry / customer service experience;
Credit/Finance experience is highly preferred;
Go-getter with mad juggling skills (or multiple hats) who can thrive in a fast-paced, agile environment;
Good at English, Cantonese and Mandarin;
Knowledge in Credit Reports/Credit Recommendations/Credit Documentation;
Good communication and interpersonal skill.

We offer attractive remuneration package, career advancement opportunities and generous fringe benefits to the right candidate.  Please apply with your full resume, salary expectation and contact phone number(s) by clicking "Apply Now".

